.TH "set_downstream_devices_error_reporting" 9 "set_downstream_devices_error_reporting" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
set_downstream_devices_error_reporting \- enable/disable the error reporting bits on the root port and its downstream ports.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" set_downstream_devices_error_reporting
.BI "(struct pci_dev *dev "  ","
.BI "bool enable "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
pointer to root port's pci_dev data structure
.IP "enable" 12
true = enable error reporting, false = disable error reporting.
